{
  "stem": "26276.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With a stick, or a lot of them had like a rubber-- with the-- a big, you know, a rubber stick with the cable inside.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If he hit with this, it hurted terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked hard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had privileges.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't sleep with us in the bunks in the room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He had his own room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He would have the kind of food like the German soldiers had.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't have to wear the uniform at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had leather boots on, like the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he did wear the band.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Or he-- I mean, he was actually like a German guard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like any other concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barracks, soldiers, no crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I just knew that I'm-- I just knew that that's going to be my life, that there's never going to be anything else, except it's going to be the rest of our lives.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never thought of being ever released or liberated, because we didn't have any paper.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know any news.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know what time it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were not working, we were able to go outside the barracks, move around outside, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] or make up something-- games inside.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We would take pieces of paper-- if you found pieces of paper-- and make cards out of it, make believe that you are playing cards.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing else.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you were especially hard-working, and the German guard would like you, he would go into the camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would report to his head above him, and once in a while they would give you some coupon-like, to be able to go in and get a couple cigarettes or some other things.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had a place-- a little tiny place-- where they would take the coupons for cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
